reviews.text: Smaller shopping mall with more higher end Chinese cuisine dining options than normal. The mall is well-connected to Hung Hom station and allows you to pass through to the hotel area near the Hung Hom promenade at the back. Good shopping but no discussion experience of visiting here.

Fortune metropolis is a shopping  centre that acts as a hub for transport. It has a train station directly opposite as well as a bus terminus. It's also a short walk to the harbour and is close to several hotels. It contains many lovely restaurants and fast food as well.
I love this place because it's the least crowded of the malls around hung hom and whampoa.  it also has educational facilities which is a plus
